blurb_text: The 2022 federal election was held on 21 May 2022. In Western Australia, the elected candidates were Sue Lines (Australian Labor Party), Michaelia Cash (Liberal), Glenn Sterle (Australian Labor Party), Dean Smith (Liberal), Dorinda Cox (The Greens (WA)), and Fatima Payman (Australian Labor Party).
